---
description: Project context for auth technical test
globs: ["**/*.ts", "**/*.tsx"]
alwaysApply: true
---

- Framework: Next.js 16+ App Router with TypeScript
- Auth: Server-side Authorization Code flow, NO next-auth
- Tokens stored in iron-session encrypted httpOnly cookies
- Mock IdP inside the same app under /api/idp/*
- All token operations are server-only, never exposed to client
- Styling: Tailwind CSS, clean and minimal
- Use named exports for utilities, default exports for pages/components
